bio.openEndedText: Aloha I’m Nick, I’m automotive enthusiast, mechanic and racer. I’ve been in auto business for over 10 years.  My dream is have a race team, but it’s expensive so I do what I need to do. All my cars in good mechanical condition, cleaned up, safe to go wherever you take it.

🌟I am an 9 year 4.9/5 Star average Turo Power Host with over 6,930 rentals under my belt. My response time to Turo messages and bookings is under 1 minute! Read my reviews and be assured you are getting THE BEST customer service available here on Turo.

🚙I'm pretty OCD and my cars are ALWAYS washed, vacuumed, and filled up before each rental. No worries about getting a sandy or dirty car from me.

✈I live just 3.5 miles from the airport so Ubering to and from the airport is quick, easy, and cheap.

🆓I even give free rides to the airport after you return my car IF I am available !

🚗Please make sure you scroll down and read the car details and guidelines sections BEFORE booking my cars. Thanks!

Aloha Turo Guest!

Mahalo for checking out the vehicles listed on Turo.

I am Marta, born in Poland, and Oahu has been my home for over 4 years now.

I love to explore the world and meet new people. Hiking, trekking, camping, and swimming are my favorite pastimes.

I used to managed vacation rentals in Waikiki (Tropical Studios at Marine Surf), I’n occasionally helping a Polish tour and travel agency (Hawaii Polonia Tours), and now, I have the pleasure of sharing my vehicles with you.

My adventure with Turo started earlier this year. My 15-passenger tour vans (aka "Hawajobus" in Polish :) ) were waiting idle for international travel to return. The idea came to at least let other families and groups have fun and use them to explore this wondrous island.

All my vehicles are available for contactless delivery anywhere on Oahu. My "home base" is in the very center of Waikiki, so I am able and happy to offer my renters both

*** DELIVERY ANYWHERE IN WAIKIKI *** and/or *** EXTREMELY CONVENIENT AND FLEXIBLE FREE PICK UP & DROP OFF IN HEART OF WAIKIKI ***

I keep all my vehicles in impeccable mechanical condition, sanitize them thoroughly before each new pick-up, and I try to make the entire "Turo Experience" as fun, easy, and positive as possible.

I greatly appreciate your consideration of reserving one of the awesome vehicles from my Polish-Hawaiian Ohana (family).

Mahalo!!! Thank you!!! Dziekujemy!!! Marta

Me and my Princess  Paveena live a fun and exciting life I work as a construction superintendent she’s a bartender so schedules allow us to almost always check in or check out vehicles we keep updating our selection of vehicles currently we have A Toyota, and a jeep gladiator Rubicon and a BMW M8 competition  they will be listed shortly we lived here in Hawaii since 1996 worked here in Honolulu for the last six years

Raf and I love the idea of ride sharing, we have rented our cars out for almost 10 years. All our vehicles fit our family of 4 safely and comfortably.  We have a Nissan Pathfinder(our beater island car/ super cheap/ fits 7), Toyota 4Runner (fits 7 adults), BMW hybrid X5 (fits 5, super stocked on everything, you can drive in the carpool lane), BMW convertible (fits 4).

Hawaii is home. If you have any questions regarding the area feel free to ask away! We know all the secret beaches and Hikes!

I have some pictures of beautiful hawaii on my IG follow @mermaid.ninja or @rainbow.ranch.hawaii

Feel free to text or WhatsA me with any questions prior to booking (sixtwosix)252.1804

📞Phone: (8O8) 206-4908

Aloha-We are the owners and operators of Honolulu Exotics and WeedriveTesla the first luxury and Electric Car rental on Oahu! We would like to share our zero emission luxury vehicles with you. 

We have the BEST selection of Tesla’s that offer features that include but not limited to the following:  22’s, full enhanced auto pilot, P100D, Ludicrous (0-60/2.4&2.8 sec), ceramic nano diamond coat, longer range, CHAdeMo, & many additional UPGRADES that other Tesla’s don’t have. **For more information on our Tesla's and questions about charging locations around the island visit www.weedrivetesla.com**

Mahalo- 

Honolulu Exotics Team

Aloha .. 

My wife and I are Local business owner/operators, Veterinarian, Parents & Surfers (ask about surf lessons) With 4 children, three girls and the youngest a boy. We are huge car enthusiasts and offer unique luxury sports vehicles for your enjoyment! Most All the vehicles we offer are rarer top models high horsepower 500 hp plus luxury and performance vehicles and are our personal vehicles that we have decided to share to offset costs, we arent a rental car business and both my wife and I work full time. With children in mind it’s hard having anything nice/excessive and justifying it, especially high end performance vehicles. Our goal is provide you with your dream car on your dream vacation and we aim to do so at an affordable fair price and we drive whatever is not rented at the time. I price our vehicles well below fair market value considering what they are enabling folks who may not normally be able to afford such a vehicle the opportunity to enjoy it for a few days/weeks!  We always strive to make sure our guests have a good experience and it’s important to us you are happy because a happy guest will cherish our vehicles as much as we do and hopefully recommend us to family and Friends and also return to us when coming back to Oahu. I had aspirations to turn this into a good profitable business but honestly we really have only just been able to make ends meet and overall are in the red still but we are car enthusiasts and would have most these vehicles no matter what because soon we will have 7 drivers in the hosehold so if we can offset the cost it helps as long as our guest are happy and are good and take care  of our vehicles we will be here for years to come since we do have a family 0f seven we need several vehicles anyway. So for now this whole thing works. We may have to switch to all Jeeps or less hot sports cars when the kids first start driving but for now you can enjoy these high end luxury sports vehicles and Hopefully with good guests like the yourselves we can make this thing last and make other peoples dream a reality weather it’s for a day or weeks at a time! 

My wife, children and I enjoy meeting new people..🏄 we also enjoy giving surf lessons. If interested ask about surf lessons or if your an avia surfer already maybe i can take you to some of my favorite spots!

Aloha 🌺

Please feel free to text any questions you have. Please send me your flight information after you get confirmation of the booking so I can coordinate with you.
Please return the car charged as much as you can before you drive to the airport, so the next guest or I can have enough miles to get to where they need to go.

Aloha And Mahalo for booking with me! I am a Hawai’i Resident and full time father to a beautiful little girl. You should feel very happy to know that your money is going to a local family and not a corporation. I strive to provide the best experience for all of my guests. Get ready to be amazed by the beauty that Hawai’i has to offer. All of my vehicles have 24 hr roadside assistance to give you the ultimate peace of mind during your trip. Mahalo Nui Loa & Ke Akua Pū 🤙🏽

It's a privilege to have purpose in life.  Responsibility, is a required (and welcomed) element to effectively produce desired results.  There is a sense of gratification once you've provided great service to another.  Being a successful small business owner is a lifestyle.  Yes it is 24/7 for those who care enough to give all they have (which will never be enough).  Sacrifices are made to create value for what is sowed.  Without those sacrifices the returns (great or small) would have little to no meaning.  This lifestyle is a choice and is by no means out of necessity.  For me, I am surrounded by good friends and literal family all the time.  Most of my clients are great people which I exhaustively enjoy interacting with on a daily basis.   So... I am actually enjoying life to the fullest and honestly wouldn't change a thing.   When a window opens, only a fool wouldn't be willing to take a moment to look out of it.  🤔 😉

人生に目的を持てる事は素晴らしい事です。責任感は、望ましい結果を効果的に出す為に必要な要素です。お客様に素晴らしいサ-ビスを提供した後、満足感があります。企業家として成功する事が私の願いでもありライフスタイルです。勿論それは、24時間、お客様いてこそ誠心誠意を尽くす事が出来ます。
価値を生み出す為に犠牲を払う事は、それが大きいとか小さいとか全く関係ありません。
このライフスタイルは、選択であり、決して必然ではありません。私はいつもとても良い友達や幸せな家族に囲まれています。
私のお客様の殆どは私が日々、交流する事をとても喜んでくれる素晴らしい方々です。
この様な理由で、私は今の人生を最高に楽しんでおり、正直な所、何一つ変えたいとは思いません。チャンスが目の前に来た時、それを掴まないなんて私には考えられません🤔😉
